Package: nos-apps
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         nosd,
         nos-apps-runtime,
         caddy | caddy-custom
Recommends: nos-agent
Description: NithronOS App Catalog and Templates
 Provides the app catalog and templates for NithronOS applications:
 - Built-in app catalog with popular applications
 - Docker Compose templates for each app
 - JSON Schema definitions for configuration
 - App icons and metadata
 - Integration with NithronOS web UI
 .
 This package contains the catalog data and templates that define
 available applications in the NithronOS App Store.
